    sample boards, but has not yet been successful witih the 1000BASE-T
    version.  That said, the 1000BASE-SX version has been working pretty
    well.
    <p>
<pre>stge0 at pci0 dev 11 function 0: Sundance TC9021 Gigabit Ethernet, rev. 7
stge0: interrupting at irq 11
stge0: Ethernet address 00:33:07:33:1a:66
gentbi0 at stge0 phy 1: Generic ten-bit interface, rev. 0
gentbi0: 1000baseSX, 1000baseSX-FDX, auto</pre>
    <p>
